    "Consequently, it is necessary to assign NA values to the observations that are missing.",
    "Computations were performed using simplified Laplace approximation strategy in the stable version of R-INLA INLA 22.12.16.",
    "The full code and data to reproduce results are available at https://github.com/spatialstatisticsupna/Forecasting_Cancer_Incidence.",
    "In this section, we evaluate the predictive performance of the models introduced in section 3.",
    "We use lung cancer incidence and mortality data for males in England, as presented in section 2."
